Politics, movies, fashion.

404
00:42:15,933 --> 00:42:18,629
Everything but religion.

405
00:42:19,737 --> 00:42:21,068
Why not religion, Dad?

406
00:42:21,772 --> 00:42:26,436
It's rude to talk about religion. You
never know who you're gonna offend.

407
00:42:31,782 --> 00:42:34,979
Josephine actually went
to the Congo last year.

408
00:42:36,620 --> 00:42:38,679
Oh, so you know.

409
00:42:54,338 --> 00:42:56,772
Hello.

410
00:42:56,941 --> 00:42:59,307
Hi. How are you feeling?

411
00:43:00,277 --> 00:43:03,610
Oh, I was dreaming.

412
00:43:04,148 --> 00:43:06,639
What were you dreaming about?

413
00:43:07,718 --> 00:43:10,744
Oh, I don't usually remember...

414
00:43:10,921 --> 00:43:15,255
...unless they're especially portentous.
Do you know what that word means?

415
00:43:15,559 --> 00:43:18,687
It means when you dream about
something that's gonna happen.

416
00:43:19,430 --> 00:43:21,921
Like one night, I had a dream...

417
00:43:22,099 --> 00:43:26,866
...where this crow came and said:

418
00:43:27,037 --> 00:43:29,528
